<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="abc.css"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8" /><h1>How This Franchisee Is Giving Hope -- and Jobs -- to the Disabled Community</h1>
				
					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="How This Franchisee Is Giving Hope -- and Jobs -- to the Disabled Community" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20160404192858-tim-hortons.jpeg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
									<div class="h5n text-medgrey">
